com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore

Class SnomedRefSetEditingContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.CDOEditingContext
      • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.BaseSnomedEditingContext
        • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.SnomedRefSetEditingContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class SnomedRefSetEditingContext
extends BaseSnomedEditingContext
    SNOMED CT reference set editing context. Delegates to SnomedEditingContext to persist the identifier concept when persisting a new reference set. On the other hand, removing a reference set doesn't automatically remove its identifier concept.

    This editing context differs in construction from all other editing context classes – it is mandatory to call #createInstance() or createInstance(IBranchPath) instead of its constructor to obtain an instance, if a SnomedEditingContext instance is not already present for use.

    See Also:
    SnomedEditingContext.getRefSetEditingContext()
